        "subject": "LU-12287 lnet: handling device failure by IB event handler",
        "message": "LU-12287 lnet: handling device failure by IB event handler\n\nThe following IB events cannot be handled by QP event handler\n- IB_EVENT_DEVICE_FATAL\n- IB_EVENT_PORT_ERR\n- IB_EVENT_PORT_ACTIVE\n\nIB event handler handles device errors such as hardware errors\nand link down.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/35037\nLustre-commit: c6e4c21c4f8b04abc53c1010a697eb3ada4fb315\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Tatsushi Takamura <takamr.tatsushi@jp.fujitsu.com>\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <ashehata@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I9869fb1cd1172040e0dd34828318017a0f30df81\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_12"
    }
